These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, climbing, water-polo
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
House: cape-cod, gothic-revival, palace
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the palace house is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Sport         | climbing | rowing   | water-polo   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| House   | palace  | cape-cod    | gothic-revival      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, november, june
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, japanese, pakistani
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, puzzles
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the pakistani##1
4. the person eating kale is the japanese##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Birthday   | november     | june     | january      |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | japanese | australian |
| Hobby           | puzzles | magic-tricks     | hiking       |

