.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
3 different games are played: whist, canasta, mah-jongg
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, badminton, sailing
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who's sport is sailing##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating kale##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Game           | mah-jongg | whist  | canasta   |
| Sport   | golf  | badminton    | sailing |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

