The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, woodworking, video-games
House: victorian, cape-cod, futuristic
1. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the paramedic and the person who's hobby is camping##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Hobby     | woodworking   | video-games | camping        |
| House   | futuristic | victorian     | cape-cod      |

