The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
There are 3 different nationalities: german, dutch, colombian
3 different pets are kept: bird, dog, hamster
1. the colombian is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the colombian and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Color          | grey    | purple     | amber      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Nationality   | colombian  | dutch       | german       |
| Pet           | dog     | bird       | hamster     |

