.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, chestnut, lilac
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, 7up
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person drinking sprite is between the person who likes chestnut and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Color          | chestnut | mauve | lilac    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | sprite     | 7up        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

