.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, indie, punk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, brown, purple
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the fan of indie is between the person eating radish and the person who likes blue##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
5. the fan of indie is between the fan of punk and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Music-Genre         | reggae | indie | punk |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Color     | purple         | brown  | blue       |

