.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, water
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, swisher-climbing
3 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, chess
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, blend, swisher
1. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person drinking water##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | soy-milk      | water      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | swisher-climbing | chess      |
| Game           | chess | backgammon     | mah-jongg |
| Cigar   | blend     | swisher          | oliveros       |

