.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, may, september
There 3 different types of food: carrot, papaya, peas
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, nigerian, russian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, orchid
1. the person who growsorchid is between the nigerian and the russian##2
2. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
4. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
5. the indian is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
6. the person who growsiris is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | february      | may | september     |
| Food          | papaya   | carrot      | peas     |
| Nationality   | russian  | indian      | nigerian |
| Flower     | bellflower | orchid        | iris     |

