There are 3 different favourite colors: white, blue, emerald
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, zucchini, pineapple
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who likes blue is between the person who likes white and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person eating pineapple is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person eating zucchini is the person who likes emerald##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who likes white##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
| Color         | emerald | blue | white |
| Food       | zucchini      | pineapple         | nectarine |
| Transport   | roller        | taxi            | scooter  |

