.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
City: prague, boston, marseilles
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, purple, emerald
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
3. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
4. the person who likes purple is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| City      | marseilles     | boston | prague      |
| Hobby         | reading  | writing       | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| Color   | white | purple    | emerald     |

