.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, rugby, cricket
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, disco, country
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of country##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea      | tea            |
| Sport           | baseball | cricket | rugby |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | techno    | country        |

