.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, june, january
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, raspberry
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, airplane, motorbike
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person watching disaster movies and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Birthday      | june    | january          | september |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Transport           | airplane | motorbike | van         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

