.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, mah-jongg
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, water
3 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, pony
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, ship, train
1. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the train and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person playing canasta##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Game   | backgammon | canasta  | mah-jongg     |
| Beverage   | water    | milk | hot-chocolate |
| Pet           | dog        | pony   | hamster  |
| Transport     | train      | ship   | airplane |

