.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, writer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, thriller
3 different games are played: poker, scrabble, billiard
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, mexican, chinese
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the spanish##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the writer is between the engineer and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Job           | lawyer   | writer   | engineer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Game   | scrabble     | poker      | billiard    |
| Nationality           | spanish | mexican | chinese    |

