.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, rowing, climbing
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
3 different games are played: monopoly, bridge, go
1. the person playing bridge is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the fan of disco is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the fan of reggae is the person playing go##1
5. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's sport is rowing and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Sport      | skateboarding | climbing     | rowing        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Game           | go           | monopoly    | bridge       |

