.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
House: palace, farmhouse, cape-cod
3 different games are played: billiard, poker, whist
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the farmhouse house is the person driving the car##1
3. the person playing poker is the person driving the car##1
4. the person playing billiard is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the cape-cod house is between the person driving the tram and the person playing poker##2
6. the person playing whist is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| House         | farmhouse     | cape-cod    | palace        |
| Game       | poker | whist   | billiard   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 